00057 void *BM_iter_at_index(BMesh *bm, const char itype, void *data, int index)
00058 {
00059     BMIter iter;
00060     void *val;
00061     int i;
00062 
00063     /* sanity check */
00064     if (index < 0) {
00065         return NULL;
00066     }
00067 
00068     val = BM_iter_new(&iter, bm, itype, data);
00069 
00070     i = 0;
00071     while (i < index) {
00072         val = BM_iter_step(&iter);
00073         i++;
00074     }
00075 
00076     return val;
00077 }

00086 int BM_iter_as_array(BMesh *bm, const char itype, void *data, void **array, const int len)
00087 {
00088     int i = 0;
00089 
00090     /* sanity check */
00091     if (len > 0) {
00092         BMIter iter;
00093         void *ele;
00094 
00095         for (ele = BM_iter_new(&iter, bm, itype, data); ele; ele = BM_iter_step(&iter)) {
00096             array[i] = ele;
00097             i++;
00098             if (i == len) {
00099                 return len;
00100             }
00101         }
00102     }
00103 
00104     return i;
00105 }

00202 void  bmiter__face_of_vert_begin(BMIter *iter)
00203 {
00204     init_iterator(iter);
00205     iter->count = 0;
00206     if (iter->vdata->e)
00207         iter->count = bmesh_disk_facevert_count(iter->vdata);
00208     if (iter->count) {
00209         iter->firstedge = bmesh_disk_faceedge_find_first(iter->vdata->e, iter->vdata);
00210         iter->nextedge = iter->firstedge;
00211         iter->firstloop = bmesh_radial_faceloop_find_first(iter->firstedge->l, iter->vdata);
00212         iter->nextloop = iter->firstloop;
00213     }
00214 }
00215 void  *bmiter__face_of_vert_step(BMIter *iter)
00216 {
00217     BMLoop *current = iter->nextloop;
00218 
00219     if (iter->count && iter->nextloop) {
00220         iter->count--;
00221         iter->nextloop = bmesh_radial_faceloop_find_next(iter->nextloop, iter->vdata);
00222         if (iter->nextloop == iter->firstloop) {
00223             iter->nextedge = bmesh_disk_faceedge_find_next(iter->nextedge, iter->vdata);
00224             iter->firstloop = bmesh_radial_faceloop_find_first(iter->nextedge->l, iter->vdata);
00225             iter->nextloop = iter->firstloop;
00226         }
00227     }
00228     
00229     if (!iter->count) iter->nextloop = NULL;
00230 
00231     return current ? current->f : NULL;
